tundra elk~
an massive tundra elk~
An imposing elk is towering here, head down sniffing the ground. 
~
The elks antlers are nearly as long as its enormous body.  The power that this
creature holds cannot be easily described as the strong muscles in its body
flex with each movement.  Its thick grey-brown coat glimmers in the sunlight
and it is a wonder a creature so beautiful even exists in this cruel
environment.  
~
