Svalbad reindeer~
a Svalbad reindeer~
A reindeer stands here sniffing the air and peering around with eyes that seem to be nearly human.
~
The Svalbad reindeer stands tall enough to rest its head upon a Vikings
shoulders.  Its brown and red coat clearly keeps it warm in the bitter cold of
its environment.  Its black nose is wet as it stiffs the air and the enormous
antlers that adorns the top of its head look like they could cause mortal
damage to any foe.  
~
