white fox~
a pure white fox~
A fox with a coat of pure white watches with intelligent eyes from the safety of its burrow. 
~
The most remarkable part of this fox is its pure white fur, that is likely one
of the best insulating mechanics of the natural world.  It moves, or slinks
around cautiously, but appears as if it could sprint off in seconds if
spooked.  Razor sharp teeth adorn the jaws of this majestic creature.  
~
